### Search active Chart of Accounts
GET {{HostAddress}}/chartofaccount/search?searchTerm=COA&showHidden=true
Accept: application/json

### Create Account
POST {{HostAddress}}/account
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ChartOfAccountId": "ab4a3724-8b1c-4fa9-ada0-462c7c132cbf",
