### Get all active Accounts by Chart of Account Id
GET {{HostAddress}}/account/GetAll?ChartOfAccountId=ab4a3724-8b1c-4fa9-ada0-462c7c132cbf
Accept: application/json

### Get all Accounts by Chart of Account Id
GET {{HostAddress}}/account/GetAll?ChartOfAccountId=ab4a3724-8b1c-4fa9-ada0-462c7c132cbf&ShowHidden=true
